Governor Abubakar Atiku Bagudu of Kebbi State has lost his younger brother, Alhaji Faruk Bagudu.
He died in the early hours of Thursday in his residence in Birnin Kebbi after a brief illness.
Farok died at the age of 56 , living behind one wife and four children.
Untill his death Alhaji Faruku was the Managing Director of Jihab Communication Limited.
And he has since been buried according to Islamic rites.
